Interface ILevelFrame

All Known Implementing Classes:
LevelEditorFrame, LevelFrame
public interface ILevelFrame
Interface representing a level frame in the game. This interface is responsible for rendering the level objects and checking the game status.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type
    Method
    Description
    void
    drawLevelObjects()
    Renders the level objects on the screen.
    void
    checkGameStatus()
    Checks the game status to determine if the game is over or if the player has won.

  • Method Details

    • drawLevelObjects

      void drawLevelObjects()
      Renders the level objects on the screen. This method is responsible for drawing all the objects in the current level.

    • checkGameStatus

      void checkGameStatus()
      Checks the game status to determine if the game is over or if the player has won. This method should be called periodically to update the game state.
